response.overview: Let All Naysayers Know.  LANK is a motto and movement started by Jalen Milroe and Terrion Arnold during the 2023 college football season. After fighting through adversity early in the season, Jalen and Terrion took a motivational phrase within the Alabama football team and turned it into one of the most prolific examples of NIL in college sports.  Premiering Friday, August 2nd at 2:00 PM Central.
response.title: LANK: The Documentary
